  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200&deg;C/ 180&deg;C (fan)/ 395&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p>Boil a full kettle</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Cut the <strong>leek<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways and wash carefully to remove any grit from between the leaves</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Slice the <strong>leek<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely, discarding the tough tops, outer leaves and root end<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></span></p>\r\n<p>Peel and slice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/summer-pea-shoot-and-leek-soup-feta-and-croutons/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a medium-sized pot over a low heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced leek</strong>&nbsp;and <strong>onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 8-10 min or until softened&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/summer-pea-shoot-and-leek-soup-feta-and-croutons/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, tear the <strong>mini baguette rolls</strong> into small bite-sized pieces&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>baguette pieces</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until golden and crisp &ndash; these are your <strong>croutons</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/summer-pea-shoot-and-leek-soup-feta-and-croutons/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong><span class=\"text-danger\">&nbsp;</span>in 800ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/summer-pea-shoot-and-leek-soup-feta-and-croutons/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>leek</strong>&nbsp;and <strong>onion</strong> has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic&nbsp;</strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>\r\n<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and cook for 5 min</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/summer-pea-shoot-and-leek-soup-feta-and-croutons/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and&nbsp;chop them roughly</p>\r\n<p>Crumble the <strong>feta&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/summer-pea-shoot-and-leek-soup-feta-and-croutons/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the 5 min, add the <strong>pea shoots</strong> and most of the <strong>chopped mint</strong> (save some for garnish!)</p>\r\n<p>Transfer everything to a <strong>food processor</strong> and blitz until smooth &ndash; this is your <strong>pea shoot &amp; leek soup</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/summer-pea-shoot-and-leek-soup-feta-and-croutons/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top&nbsp;the <strong>pea shoot &amp; leek soup</strong>&nbsp;with the <strong>croutons</strong> and <strong>crumbled feta</strong></p>\r\n<p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining mint leaves</strong>,&nbsp;the <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(Can't handle the heat? Go easy!)&nbsp;and a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
